    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">You gain unmatched predictive combat senses. When you would cast a Hyūga Hijutsu as a reaction to taking damage, the jutsu gains a bonus 4 DR, based on the rank it is cast for the duration for the jutsu. (D-Rank/C-Rank: 4 DR, B-Rank/A-Rank: 8 DR, S-Rank: 12 DR).</span></p>",
